Airtel Zambia Says to Build More Transmission Towers to Boost Market Share

-- B y   A n t h o n y   M u k w i t a
-- 
2011-07-21T14:36:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/airtel-zambia-says-to-build-more-transmission-towers-to-boost-market-share.html
Bharti Airtel Ltd. (BHARTI) ’s Zambian unit,
the southern African country’s biggest mobile-phone operator,
will build 200 more transmission towers by the end of the year
to help boost market share, Managing Director Fayaz King said.  The increase will raise the number of towers to 1,000, King
told reporters today in Lusaka, the capital. The company aims to
increase its market share to 80 percent from about 70 percent,
he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
